      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お願いしまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nice to meet you~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5072335481643675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 4.5405668814977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日から、二人を担当する{user}です\n一緒に頑張っていきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m {user}‚ and I'm in charged of you two.\nI’m excited to be working with both of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.873900214831034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "では、今日は事務所を案内した後\n二人が生活する寮に案内します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I’ll be giving you a tour of the agency‚\nthen I’ll show you around the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5405668814977,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3533.333333333369,
          "startTime": 15.073900214831069
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 14.773900214831034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……ここが事務所……\n随分小さいのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is the agency…\nA bit…small.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.27390021483104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "一応スタジオも併設されているから練習は出来る\nただ、本格的な練習は東京で行うことになるけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have our own in-house studio‚ so you can practice there.\nAlthough your more intensive lessons will be in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.640566881497712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "東京？　通うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tokyo? Do you mean we have to commute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.50723354816438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "週二回ね。いい先生は向こうに行かないといないから\nもちろん、学校の授業に影響のないようにする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Twice a week‚ yes. All the best teachers are in Tokyo.\nAnd you’ll have to keep up your grades in school‚ of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.37390021483105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい\n分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nUnderstood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.373900214831046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……三枝さんは同行するんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will Saegusa-san be joining us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.60723354816438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今の所その予定はない……\nけどダンスの先生は三枝さんも信頼している有名な方だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not in the plan‚ no.\nBut he has a lot of faith in your dance coach.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.99798187414806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんの紹介がなければ\n新人は見てもらえないような人気の先生だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s very popular and in demand.\nI doubt she’d agree to instruct rookies if it weren’t for Saegusa-san’s pull.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.231315207481394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.831315207481396,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3199.9999999999886,
          "startTime": 63.031315207481384
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 61.797981874148064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ここがレッスン室。防音設備も整っているから\nボイストレーニングなども行える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is your lesson room. It’s soundproofed‚ too‚\nso you can do vocal training in here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5313152074814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.99798187414805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "誰……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.86464854081473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.0313152074814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（この二人組、間違いない……LizNoirだ）\n（今や若手トップと言われる有名なグループ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I know these two girls… They’re LizNoir.）\n（They’re considered the top newcomer group.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.66464854081474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.83131520748142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.66464854081477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの……LizNoirの二人ですよね\nどうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ hi. You’re LizNoir.\nAnything you need?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "悪い、たまたま近くに来たから寄ってくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ they were in the neighborhood and decided to swing by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昔のよしみで、な",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To catch up‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "…………三枝さん、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう、その話は終わったと言っただろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already told you. I’ve said all there is to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺がバンプロに戻ることはない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not going to go back to Van Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロ……？\nバンプロダクションのことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Van?\nDo you mean Van Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（バンプロダクションといえば）\n（日本でもトップクラスの芸能事務所だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Van Productions.）\n（It‘s one of the top-tier talent agencies in all of Japan.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんが星見プロを設立する前に所属し）\n（LizNoirを見出した事務所でもある）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s where Saegusa-san worked before establishing Hoshimi Productions‚）\n（and it’s also the agency that discovered LizNoir.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "私達がバンプロから独立して\nここに移籍しても無理ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can’t we leave Van Productions\nand sign with you instead?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バカなことは考えるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be stupid.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなことをしたら、朝倉が黙っているはずないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know Asakura won’t take that lying down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人は朝倉のもとでしっかり頑張ればいい",
